reviewText: I have given a five stat rating because the seller included the concert video as well as the cd of music.  I was thrilled due to the fact I had never seen the adoration and worship of all these young people.  What a treasure for me to have this.  Thank you and know the excellent service is greatly appreciated here.
Irvin Baxter makes understanding  prophecy easy,.  I would highly recommend this DVD.  If you enjoy prophecy, you will enjoy this.
